text: The Diocese of Vibiana is a suppressed and titular see of the Roman Catholic Church in North Africa. Vibiana. The current bishop is Eliseo Antonio Ariotti who was appointed 17 Jul 2003,Le Petit Episcopian, Issue 173, Number 14,471. and who replaced Angelo Palmas (1964-2003). ==References== Category:Catholic titular sees in Africa Category:Former Roman Catholic dioceses in Africa
title: Diocese of Vibiana
